para.verbatim:
Parameter:  String (unicode or bytes).
Returns:    The `text`, with after processing the following backslash
            escape sequences. This is useful if you want to force a "dumb"
            quote or other character to appear.

            Escape  Value
            ------  -----
            \\      &#92;
            \"      &#34;
            \'      &#39;
            \.      &#46;
            \-      &#45;
            \`      &#96;
